# Shallow Clone

## Clone specific branch
Only the default branch will be checked out if `--branch` is not provided
```sh
git clone --depth 1 --single-branch --branch BRANCH REPO
# ghq
ghq --shallow --branch BRANCH REPO
```

## Fetch branches after shallow clone
```sh
# Specific branch
git remote set-branches --add origin BRANCH
# All branches
git remote set-branches origin '*'
```
